name: tRNA (guanosine18-2'-O)-methyltransferase
reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + guanosine18 in tRNA = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + 2'-O-methylguanosine18 in tRNA [RN:R02917]
comment: The enzyme catalyses the methylation of guanosine18 in tRNA.
